trans-unit.source: Machine Learning Studio: Algorithm and Module Help
trans-unit.target: Machine Learning Studio: Algorithm and Module Help

trans-unit.source: Microsoft Azure Machine Learning Studio is a collaborative visual development environment that enables you to build, test, and deploy predictive analytics solutions that operate on your data.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft Azure Machine Learning Studio is a collaborative visual development environment that enables you to build, test, and deploy predictive analytics solutions that operate on your data.

trans-unit.source: The Machine Learning service and development environment is cloud-based, provides compute resource and memory flexibility, and eliminates setup and installation concerns because you work through your web browser.
trans-unit.target: The Machine Learning service and development environment is cloud-based, provides compute resource and memory flexibility, and eliminates setup and installation concerns because you work through your web browser.

trans-unit.source: This reference material supplements the Azure Machine Learning documentation that you can find in the <externalLink><linkText>Machine Learning Documentation Center</linkText><linkUri>http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/services/machine-learning/</linkUri></externalLink>.
trans-unit.target: This reference material supplements the Azure Machine Learning documentation that you can find in the <externalLink><linkText>Machine Learning Documentation Center</linkText><linkUri>http://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/services/machine-learning/</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: The documentation here provides detailed technical information about the modules that are available in <externalLink><linkText>Azure Machine Learning Studio</linkText><linkUri>https://studio.azureml.net/Home</linkUri></externalLink>.
trans-unit.target: The documentation here provides detailed technical information about the modules that are available in <externalLink><linkText>Azure Machine Learning Studio</linkText><linkUri>https://studio.azureml.net/Home</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: This technical reference for Azure Machine Learning contains the following sections.
trans-unit.target: This technical reference for Azure Machine Learning contains the following sections.

trans-unit.source: These topics describe each of the modules available in Azure Machine Learning Studio, including the input requirements, typical outputs, use cases, parameters for customizing the behavior of individual modules, and examples of how the module is used in the Azure <externalLink><linkText>Model Gallery</linkText><linkUri>http://gallery.azureml.net/</linkUri></externalLink>, technical background on the machine learning algorithms, and other implementation details.
